Title: The Hopf Algebra Structure of Connes and Kreimer in Epstein-Glaser
  Renormalization
Authors: G. Pinter
Comments: 8 pages
Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 54 (2000) 227-233
\\
  We show how the Hopf algebra structure of renormalization discovered by
Kreimer can be found in the Epstein-Glaser framework without using an analogue
of the forest formula of Zimmermann.
